Vol / Page: 5
Edition:
Quote: In vain did the sole kick; the schnapper snapped to no purpose; the trunk of the elephant fish thrashed the prison bars, and they broke not; the soldierfish made a bayonet charge against the thin brown lines, but they did not give way; the squid spilled more ink than Wellington's most prolific newspaper correspondent, but it made no impression on the meshes.
